{"word":"Ahab","slug":"ahab","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Ahab</b> <a href=\"#/H256\">H256</a> <br/> 1. King of Israel<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=16&verse=29'>1Ki 16:29</a> <br/> - Marries Jezebel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=16&verse=31'>1Ki 16:31</a> <br/> - Idolatry of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=16&verse=33'>1Ki 16:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=18&verse=19'>1Ki 18:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=21&verse=26'>1Ki 21:26</a> <br/> - Other wickedness of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=3&verse=2'>2Ki 3:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=21&verse=6'>2Ch 21:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=22&verse=4'>2Ch 22:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=33&chapter=6&verse=16'>Mic 6:16</a> <br/> - Reproved by Elijah. Assembles the prophets of Baal<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=18&verse=46'>1Ki 18:46</a> <br/> - Fraudulently confiscates Naboth's vineyard<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=21'>1Ki 21</a> <br/> - Defeats Ben-Hadad<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=20'>1Ki 20</a> <br/> - Closing history and death of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=22'>1Ki 22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=18'>2Ch 18</a> <br/> - Succeeded by his son, Ahaziah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=22&verse=40'>1Ki 22:40</a> <br/> - Prophecies against<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=20&verse=42'>1Ki 20:42</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=21&verse=24'>1Ki 21:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=22&verse=28'>1Ki 22:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=9&verse=8'>2Ki 9:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=9&verse=26'>2Ki 9:26</a> <br/> - Sons of, murdered<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=10&verse=8'>2Ki 10:8</a> <br/> 2. A false prophet<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=29&verse=22'>Jer 29:22</a>"}]}